# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# ANTS 2.0 Commit Message Template (I-NEW-17 · K.22 · 29 Apr 2026)
# Owner: HoEng #21 + CCVO #52 + #63 FJA-CDCA
# Install: git config commit.template .gitmessage
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#
# Format (replace placeholder lines · keep section headers):
#
# K.<x>: <one-line summary · imperative · ≤72 chars>
#
# - <substantive change 1>
# - <substantive change 2>
# - <substantive change 3>
#
# ARAI:
# A: <action — what was done>
# R: <result — what changed · measurable>
# I: <idea improvement — what's next · or "none">
#
# Refs: <I-NEW-XX or feedback memory file or "none">
#
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Conventions:
# - First line MUST start with K.<x>: (sweep marker · enables changelog-builder.py to parse)
# - Use Thai or English freely · be specific not abstract
# - List 2–5 substantive changes · skip trivia (formatting · whitespace)
# - ARAI block mandatory if commit changes operational logic or canonical fact
# - Refs links to I-NEW spec or memory file that motivated this commit
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
